 between the two models became greater than a dollar assuming that the account
 started with $1 of debt and that model 1 was calculated with a daily compoundin
g rate.
 These models were calculated with intrest rates of 6.9%, 12.99%, and 19.99%.
 The results of these calculations are shown in the below table 1.
